reason.er.objects

Class Predicate<T,U>

  • java.lang.Object
    • reason.er.objects.Predicate<T,U>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - generic
    U - generic
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Concept, Role

    public abstract class Predicate<T,U>
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class that describes all Predicate Objects. Predicates have a label, terms, a scope, a size, and can be negated.
    Author:
    Aaron Eberhart
